<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="quarter-n">quarter <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'kwɔːtə(r)/    美 /'kwɔːrtər/  </p>
<p>[C]</p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>四分之一；(橄榄球赛等的) 四分之一场：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>Three quarters of</strong> the students in our class are League members.
我们班四分之三的学生是团员。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The Rockets led by two points going into <strong>the fourth quarter</strong>.
火箭队以领先两分的优势进入第四节。</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.★ <strong>一刻钟：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I got up at <strong>a quarter to</strong> seven.
我6点45分起床。</p></div>

<h4 id="3">3.<strong>季度；付款的季度：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>He pays at the end of each quarter.
他在每个季度末付款。</p></div>

<h4 id="4">4.<strong>(美国和加拿大的) 两角五分的硬币</strong></h4></div>